===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}}, equivalent to {{m|en|yond}} (from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|ġeond}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{m|gem-pro|*jend-}}, {{m|gem-pro|*jand-}}) + {{m|en|-er}}, as in {{m|en|hither}}, {{m|en|thither}}. Cognate with Dutch {{m|nl|ginder|}} ('over there').

